<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 16:15:03 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>大眼达布斯</title><link>https://some.pics/69da738366611</link><description>&lt;p&gt;大块头达布斯和他那双大大的谷歌眼 👀&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A black dog with a red harness sits on a path beside tall grass and trees." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ericmwalk/69da738366611.jpg" width="5712"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ericmwalk.some.pics"&gt;@ericmwalk&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 16:15:03 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>某处，无处</title><link>https://some.pics/69da72070152e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;某处，无处&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A single train track on gravel is winding its way along a forest. The picture has been processed and appears in grey tones, with one single and very small red light along the tracks " height="3767" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/69da72070152e.jpg" width="2825"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 16:08:42 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>塔科阿河火车风光</title><link>https://some.pics/69da6b9b33f40</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从火车上看到的塔科阿河景色。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A serene riverside scene with clear water reflecting a bright blue sky and lush green trees lining the banks, creating a peaceful, natural setting." height="2893" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69da6b9b33f40.jpg" width="3857"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 15:41:18 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>胡佛水坝近景</title><link>https://some.pics/69da54a80ba65</link><description>&lt;p&gt;胡佛水坝，在前往拉斯维加斯的途中可见。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Aerial view of a dam system in a mountainous canyon with a large concrete arch dam holding back blue water, surrounded by rocky terrain and a highway bridge crossing the canyon above." height="2920" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mihobu/69da54a80ba65.jpg" width="2920"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mihobu.some.pics"&gt;@mihobu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 14:03:23 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>归途中的737-MAX8</title><link>https://some.pics/69da47fd4addf</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在结束了图森市的九周行程后，我正乘坐一架机龄五年的737-MAX8型客机，经拉斯维加斯转机返回哥伦布市的家中。这张照片拍摄于起飞后不久。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A Southwest Airlines aircraft wing and engine are visible in the foreground, photographed from a passenger window during flight above a thick layer of white clouds under a blue sky." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mihobu/69da47fd4addf.jpg" width="4284"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mihobu.some.pics"&gt;@mihobu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 13:09:20 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>